@startuml
[*] --> Login
Login: User details input
Login: Teacher -> TeacherArea
Login: Student -> StudentArea

TeacherArea: [*] --> CreateQuiz
CreateQuiz: Quiz creation
CreateQuiz: Save as Draft -> DraftQuiz
CreateQuiz: Post for Students -> PublishedQuiz

PublishedQuiz: [*] --> Over
Over: Quiz over
Over: Results available

DraftQuiz: [*] --> Edit
Edit: Edit quiz
Edit: Save as Draft -> DraftQuiz
Edit: Publish -> PublishedQuiz

StudentArea: Notification -> SelectQuiz
SelectQuiz: Choose a quiz
SelectQuiz: Start Quiz -> AnswerQuiz

AnswerQuiz: [*] --> Submit
Submit: Quiz submission
Submit: Results available

@enduml
